Interface PasswordMasker

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JsonPasswordMasker, UriQueryStringPasswordMasker, XmlAttributePasswordMasker

    public interface PasswordMasker
    Class that tries to mask a password in a string. The implementation tries to mask a field for a specific format, for instance JSON or XML.
